snippet.title: Ice Station Z (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Ice Station Z Gameplay Trailer for all Nintendo 3DS's.

Release Date: November 3rd 2016.

- Open World Zombie Survival
- Single Player or Multiplayer (Internet & Local)
- Internet Multiplayer with Anybody
- Internet Voice Chat & Text Chat
- Zombies, Survival, Exploration, Vehicles

Music: Underworld by Emid.
